      "modified": "2026-04-18T23:00:00.000Z",
      "content": "C2 domain remains unknown. A 32-byte XOR-encrypted blob at file offset 0x03153B64 in teams-launcher.exe contains the obfuscated C2 URL. Dynamic analysis in a Windows sandbox is required to recover it. Encrypted blob hex: 6d584a52195c4b4b564baeacaea5a892bbaca1a4a9acb9a4a2a392aea5a8aea6",
